snippet.title: HALF DEAD 3 CONFIRMED
snippet.description:
HALF DEAD 3 on STEAM: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1520380/HALF_DEAD_3/
Hello everybody!

We are glad to announce that we are at the last stage of Half dead 3 development.

Stay tuned for new news and announcements on the Half dead 3 game page. 

www.facebook.com/groups/halfdead3/
https://twitter.com/HALFDEAD_3/
